sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant CTRL as Control Abstraction
  participant Q as Command Queue
  participant DRV as Driver (WASM/JS)
  participant DEV as WebUSB Device

  UI->>CTRL: sendCommand({req_method, req_params})
  CTRL->>Q: enqueue request
  Q->>DRV: sendCommandToDevice(req)
  DRV->>DEV: device-specific control op(s)
  DEV-->>DRV: reply/status
  DRV-->>Q: normalized reply
  Q-->>CTRL: resolve/reject
  CTRL-->>UI: update state / UI
